{
    "publish_date": "2012-09-17T15:54:52.000Z", 
    "video_length": "PT6M47S", 
    "captions": [
        {
            "text": "MITT ROMNEY: Drug trafficking,\nthat&#39;s one more of those areas", 
            "dur": "2.11", 
            "start": "9.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "of concern.", 
            "dur": "0.73", 
            "start": "11.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s time for the United States\nof America to take", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "11.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "responsibility for the pain,\nand suffering, and torture,", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "14.6"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and murder that&#39;s going on\nthroughout Latin America.", 
            "dur": "3.69", 
            "start": "18.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "SHANE SMITH: Maybe one of the\nreasons that Mitt Romney is so", 
            "dur": "1.89", 
            "start": "22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "concerned with the drug wars\ntaking place just south of the", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "23.89"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "American border is that it\naffects him and his family", 
            "dur": "4.03", 
            "start": "26.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "personally.", 
            "dur": "1.11", 
            "start": "30.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hi, I&#39;m Shane Smith and we&#39;re\nhere at the VICE headquarters", 
            "dur": "2.41", 
            "start": "31.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in Williamsburg, Brooklyn.", 
            "dur": "1.17", 
            "start": "33.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now Williamsburg is ground zero\nfor hipsters, which means", 
            "dur": "3.74", 
            "start": "35.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s also ground zero for\npartying, which means it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "38.84"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "ground zero for cocaine.", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "41.95"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now VICE has talked a lot about\ncocaine over the years.", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, one of our magazine\ncovers featured a mirror with", 
            "dur": "3.88", 
            "start": "46.79"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a big line of coke\nchopped up on it.", 
            "dur": "1.61", 
            "start": "50.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But recently we followed a story\nthat made us think twice", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "52.28"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "about our historical fascination\nwith coke.", 
            "dur": "2.28", 
            "start": "55.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it has to do\nwith Mormons--", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "57.98"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "as in Mitt Romney&#39;s family\ntype Mormons--", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "59.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mexican drug cartels, polygamy,\nkidnapping, cocaine,", 
            "dur": "4.88", 
            "start": "62.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and finally, murder.", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "67.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now it&#39;s a freaky,\nfreaky story.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "69.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s taking place just\nsouth of the US border.", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "71.41"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we went to check it\nout first hand to see", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "74.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "what was going on.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "76.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "We just passed through from El\nPaso, Texas, which is actually", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "82.56"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "one of the safest cities in\nAmerica, into Juarez, Mexico,", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "85.8"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "which is actually one of\nthe most dangerous", 
            "dur": "1.28", 
            "start": "88.53"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cities in the world.", 
            "dur": "1.11", 
            "start": "89.81"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, it&#39;s the most dangerous\ncity in the world", 
            "dur": "2.07", 
            "start": "90.92"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "for journalists.", 
            "dur": "1.23", 
            "start": "92.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re driving with a camera\nrolling, which is, in", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "94.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "retrospect, very\nfucking stupid.", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "96.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "People always ask me what the\nmost dangerous place I&#39;ve ever", 
            "dur": "2.773", 
            "start": "100.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "been to is.", 
            "dur": "0.363", 
            "start": "103.523"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And when I say Mexico, they&#39;re\na bit flummoxed", 
            "dur": "2.289", 
            "start": "103.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and they say, Mexico?", 
            "dur": "1.205", 
            "start": "106.175"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been to Mexico.", 
            "dur": "0.82", 
            "start": "107.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve been to Cancun, Joe&#39;s\ntequila foam party,", 
            "dur": "3.02", 
            "start": "108.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and Boom Boom Room.", 
            "dur": "1.33", 
            "start": "111.22"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But this Mexico here in Juarez,\nis the Mexico run by", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "112.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the narco lords.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "115.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They don&#39;t care about what\nyou&#39;re shooting.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "116.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They don&#39;t walk up and say, hey,\nwhat&#39;s that camera for?", 
            "dur": "1.81", 
            "start": "118.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They just see a camera and go,\nthat can&#39;t good, and bam.", 
            "dur": "3.75", 
            "start": "119.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now the drug lords that rule\nnorthern Mexico are like most", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "123.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "mafia around the world.", 
            "dur": "0.97", 
            "start": "126.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;re very wealthy, and\nthey&#39;re insanely ruthless.", 
            "dur": "2.91", 
            "start": "127.2"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the thing that sets the\nMexican cartels apart from the", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "130.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "other mobs is their seemingly\nprofound love of murder.", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "132.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They put other crime syndicates\nto shame with the", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "138.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sheer scale of their killing,\nnot to mention the gruesome", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "140.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "eye-catching way they present\ntheir murders with a kind of", 
            "dur": "2.87", 
            "start": "143.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "evil inventiveness.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "146.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s not just traditional\ngang on gang violence either.", 
            "dur": "3.16", 
            "start": "151.42"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The cartels kill anyone and\neveryone in their way.", 
            "dur": "3.2", 
            "start": "154.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rivals, witnesses, journalists,\npoliticians, and", 
            "dur": "2.37", 
            "start": "157.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "police are all targets.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "160.15"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And rather than hiding the\nbodies like most criminals,", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "162.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "they actually want\nyou to see them.", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "164.59"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they want you to know\nexactly who did it.", 
            "dur": "4.28", 
            "start": "166.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, the war on drugs in\nMexico is so violent that its", 
            "dur": "3.58", 
            "start": "170.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "body count is almost 10 times\nthat of American soldiers", 
            "dur": "3.8", 
            "start": "174.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "killed in the real wars in\nIraq and Afghanistan.", 
            "dur": "4.36", 
            "start": "178.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And in a country where it&#39;s\nsupposedly illegal to own", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "182.67"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "guns, the narcos are armed\nto the teeth with", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "185"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "state-of-the-art weaponry, 90%\nof which are smuggled in from", 
            "dur": "4.21", 
            "start": "188.06"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the United States, which is\nsomething we got to see first", 
            "dur": "2.72", 
            "start": "192.27"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hand as soon as we arrived\nin Juarez.", 
            "dur": "2.085", 
            "start": "194.99"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MEXICAN OFFICIAL:\n[SPEAKING SPANISH]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "199.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "SHANE SMITH: We came in here and\nwe saw this huge bunker.", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "209.39"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re like, oh.", 
            "dur": "0.65", 
            "start": "212.08"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is where they hold all the\nguns, and all the drugs,", 
            "dur": "3.78", 
            "start": "212.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and everything in this big,\nmassive concrete bunker.", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "216.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they&#39;re like, no, no.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "219.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The drugs and the guns are\nhere in the trucks.", 
            "dur": "2.16", 
            "start": "219.86"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s a nightclub called\nthe Sphinx.", 
            "dur": "1.825", 
            "start": "222.02"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So last night the police caught\nthese guys trying to", 
            "dur": "4.04", 
            "start": "226.71"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "smuggle in 268,000 rounds of\nammunition in a truck with", 
            "dur": "4.68", 
            "start": "230.75"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oklahoma plates.", 
            "dur": "1.14", 
            "start": "235.43"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It was driven by a\nguy from Dallas.", 
            "dur": "2.95", 
            "start": "236.57"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Over a quarter million rounds\nof ammunition, this is the", 
            "dur": "4.06", 
            "start": "239.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "kind of firepower\nthat they have.", 
            "dur": "1.6", 
            "start": "243.58"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a .30 caliber Browning,\nwhich shoots super", 
            "dur": "2.929", 
            "start": "253.78"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fast and can shoot through\narmored cars.", 
            "dur": "2.841", 
            "start": "256.709"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then they have this\nanti-aircraft, .50 cal.", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "259.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Can I pick it up?", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "262.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER 1: No.", 
            "dur": "0.15", 
            "start": "263.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No.", 
            "dur": "0.15", 
            "start": "263.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can&#39;t touch that.", 
            "dur": "0.54", 
            "start": "263.4"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "SHANE SMITH: Shit, I did.", 
            "dur": "0.75", 
            "start": "263.94"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I put my finger on it.", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "264.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to get in trouble.", 
            "dur": "1.57", 
            "start": "266.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They just confiscated\nthese weapons.", 
            "dur": "2.19", 
            "start": "267.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I touched the .50 cal.", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "269.88"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they haven&#39;t dusted\nthem for prints yet.", 
            "dur": "1.9", 
            "start": "271.62"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So now my prints are\non a murder weapon.", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "273.52"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Not good.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "275.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MEXICAN OFFICIAL:\n[SPEAKING SPANISH]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "278.38"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MITT ROMNEY: These look like\nthey&#39;re from America.", 
            "dur": "1.95", 
            "start": "284.12"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "America, America, America, all\nthe guns are from America.", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "286.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;re all homicides?", 
            "dur": "0.9", 
            "start": "289"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They&#39;ve tested them out?", 
            "dur": "0.83", 
            "start": "289.9"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MEXICAN OFFICIAL:\n[SPEAKING SPANISH]", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "290.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "SHANE SMITH: Oh, sorry.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "294.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That was loud.", 
            "dur": "1.86", 
            "start": "299.65"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It smells very strong.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "301.51"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Holy Jesus, I know this doesn&#39;t\nlook like crazy.", 
            "dur": "2.6", 
            "start": "303.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But you can smell.", 
            "dur": "1", 
            "start": "305.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Wow, it&#39;s a lot of drugs,\ndrugs and flak jackets.", 
            "dur": "5.36", 
            "start": "306.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So this is sort of a rustic\ntype of smuggling.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "312.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "They call it a burrero, which\nis like a donkey.", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "314.7"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they just walk through\nthe desert with the", 
            "dur": "2.33", 
            "start": "316.5"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pot on their back.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "318.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the market for the\ndrugs is America.", 
            "dur": "2.79", 
            "start": "321.3"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The market for the weapons\nis here in Mexico.", 
            "dur": "2.84", 
            "start": "324.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And they go like this.", 
            "dur": "2.55", 
            "start": "326.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When you look at this, like\n.50 cals, assault rifles,", 
            "dur": "3.59", 
            "start": "329.48"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "military grade machine guns,\nyou realize, OK, how do the", 
            "dur": "4.02", 
            "start": "333.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "police fight them, let along\nregular people, let alone", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "337.09"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mormons who aren&#39;t allowed\nto own guns.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "339.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s crazy.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "341.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we&#39;re about 200 miles\nsouth of Juarez now.", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "345.37"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And we&#39;re out in the\nmiddle of nowhere.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "348.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is like the narco\nsuperhighway.", 
            "dur": "2.08", 
            "start": "350.36"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s actually 300 different\nsmuggling trails", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "352.44"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "right through here.", 
            "dur": "0.78", 
            "start": "355.05"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s no big wall\nor anything.", 
            "dur": "1.21", 
            "start": "355.83"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can just walk off into\nthe desert with your", 
            "dur": "2.3", 
            "start": "357.04"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pack full of cocaine.", 
            "dur": "1.27", 
            "start": "359.34"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, all of a sudden,\nfolks in Williamsburg and", 
            "dur": "2.295", 
            "start": "360.61"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "hipsters are doing coke.", 
            "dur": "3.195", 
            "start": "362.905"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you&#39;re out here, it kind of\ndawns on you that there&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "366.1"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "nowhere to go.", 
            "dur": "1.09", 
            "start": "368.64"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Like if something happens or\nif somebody even chases us,", 
            "dur": "3.01", 
            "start": "369.73"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "where are we going to run to?", 
            "dur": "1.52", 
            "start": "372.74"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because you can&#39;t trust\nthe police.", 
            "dur": "1.98", 
            "start": "374.26"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You especially can&#39;t trust the\nlocal police because they&#39;re", 
            "dur": "1.87", 
            "start": "376.24"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "all corrupt.", 
            "dur": "1.1", 
            "start": "378.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So basically, right now, it&#39;s\na straight shot to the", 
            "dur": "3.24", 
            "start": "379.21"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mormons, their guns,\nand their god.", 
            "dur": "2.525", 
            "start": "382.45"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ah, we&#39;ve come to\nGod&#39;s country.", 
            "dur": "4.58", 
            "start": "391.11"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER 2: Joel LeBaron\nwas killed by his", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "395.69"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "own brother, Ervil.", 
            "dur": "1.36", 
            "start": "397.87"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He started to kill in\nthe name of God.", 
            "dur": "2.88", 
            "start": "399.23"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "SHANE SMITH: That&#39;s\nsome crazy shit.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "402.11"
        }
    ], 
